  <brief_title>Cohort Study of New Prognostic Factors With Peripheral Blood and Bone Marrow Evaluation at the Time of Diagnosis and Relapse in Myelodysplastic Syndrome</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Yonsei University</agency>
